website_description:
Located on the bank of Sazava River in Tynec nad Sazavou, Hotel Tynec offers a spacious garden perfect for eating out, a fire place and barbecue facilities upon request. An on-site information centre offers an opportunity to arrange tailor-made bike trips in the surrounding.
Well-lit rooms at the Tynec offer carpeted floors, a desk and a wardrobe. Bathroom provides free toiletries and a shower. A large dance hall is located on site, while a restaurant can be found nearby. Free Wi-Fi is provided.
The property is very bicycle-friendly and offers bicycle repair service, bike and boat rentals. A cycling path, Green Way, starts on site.
River Sazava offers swimming and sunbathing opportunities, as well as canoeing and kayaking. Horseback riding and a golf course can be reached in 5 km.
Train and Bus Stop can be found in Tynec nad Sazavou, 300 m away. Aquapark in Měřín can be reached in 10 km.

website_description:
Located in Stranný, 49 km from Aquapalace, Penzion Stranny provides accommodation with a seasonal outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a bar and a shared lounge. Among the various facilities of this property are a garden and a terrace. The accommodation offers room service, and organising tours for guests.
At the guest house, each room includes a desk, a flat-screen TV, a private bathroom, bed linen and towels. Free WiFi and a seating area are available to all guests, while selected rooms are fitted with a DVD player. Guest rooms will provide guests with a wardrobe and a kettle.
Penzion Stranny offers a continental or buffet breakfast.
Guests at the accommodation will be able to enjoy activities in and around Stranný, like hiking and cycling.
The nearest airport is Vaclav Havel Prague Airport, 64 km from Penzion Stranny.
